<font color="#ffffff">Don't hurt me, Ake. Let me go.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

173
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:46,520
<font color="#ffffff">Say it again. I want to hear it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

174
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:48,800
<font color="#ffffff">I didn't say anything!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

175
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:50,120
<font color="#ffffff">Let me go!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

176
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:52,800
<font color="#ffffff">What are you doing? Ake!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

177
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:55,360
<font color="#ffffff">You got a smart mouth, huh?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

178
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:57,280
<font color="#ffffff">How's that?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

179
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:00,560
<font color="#ffffff">This is what happens</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

180
00:15:01,400 --> 00:15:02,720
<font color="#ffffff">when you run your mouth at me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

181
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:05,800
<font color="#ffffff">-Get the hell out!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Akekaphol.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

182
00:15:06,560 --> 00:15:07,760
<font color="#ffffff">You hellspawn.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

183
00:15:08,680 --> 00:15:09,680
<font color="#ffffff">One day,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

184
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:13,080
<font color="#ffffff">I'm going to make you pay for this!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

185
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:16,240
<font color="#ffffff">Go ahead.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

186
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:21,000
<font color="#ffffff">And don't think you'll ever live in peace.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

187
00:15:22,680 --> 00:15:26,200
<font color="#ffffff">Because I will kill your entire family.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

188
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,960
<font color="#ffffff">Damn it!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

189
00:15:40,040 --> 00:15:41,080
<font color="#ffffff">Akekaphol!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

190
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:42,800
<font color="#ffffff">Remember this!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

191
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:46,040
<font color="#ffffff">Karma is going to catch up to you!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

192
00:15:46,120 --> 00:15:47,960
<font color="#ffffff">You won't die a peaceful death!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

193
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:01,720
<font color="#ffffff">You called me in so early.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">It must be something important.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

194
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:06,720
<font color="#ffffff">I want you to help me speed up</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">the music production for Petch.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

195
00:16:07,560 --> 00:16:11,200
<font color="#ffffff">Me? Isn't that Ake's department?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

196
00:16:11,280 --> 00:16:12,840
<font color="#ffffff">I'll be honest with you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

197
00:16:12,920 --> 00:16:14,200
<font color="#ffffff">I don't trust Ake.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

198
00:16:14,800 --> 00:16:16,920
<font color="#ffffff">I told him to do one thing,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">and he did another.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

199
00:16:17,560 --> 00:16:21,680
<font color="#ffffff">That's why I want you</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to come help me at the company.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

200
00:16:21,760 --> 00:16:25,480
<font color="#ffffff">Your first task is to oversee</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">all of Petch's music projects.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

201
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:29,800
<font color="#ffffff">Why so quiet, Dao?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

202
00:16:29,880 --> 00:16:31,400
<font color="#ffffff">Well…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

203
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:33,280
<font color="#ffffff">It's just a bit sudden.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

204
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:35,720
<font color="#ffffff">But I'm more than happy to give it my all.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

205
00:16:35,800 --> 00:16:37,000
<font color="#ffffff">Very good.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

206
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:39,520
<font color="#ffffff">I believe you can do it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

207
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:42,760
<font color="#ffffff">Let's work together to polish Petch</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">into the true diamond he is.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

208
00:16:44,280 --> 00:16:45,600
<font color="#ffffff">Of course.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

209
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:01,480
<font color="#ffffff">You didn't forget anything?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

210
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:04,119
<font color="#ffffff">No, Petch. That's everything.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

211
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,040
<font color="#ffffff">Okay.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

212
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:09,599
<font color="#ffffff">Thinking about it makes me a bit sad.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

213
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:12,359
<font color="#ffffff">The three of us</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">used to live here together.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

214
00:17:13,280 --> 00:17:17,280
<font color="#ffffff">Now it's just you and me</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">moving in with Mr. Nop.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

215
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:35,280
<font color="#ffffff">Hey.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

216
00:17:35,360 --> 00:17:36,760
<font color="#ffffff">Why are you crying all of a sudden?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

217
00:17:37,280 --> 00:17:38,520
<font color="#ffffff">What's wrong, Sai?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

218
00:17:40,840 --> 00:17:42,360
<font color="#ffffff">If we don't count Dam,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

219
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:43,720
<font color="#ffffff">you're the only one</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

220
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:46,160
<font color="#ffffff">who's truly been good to me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

221
00:17:47,560 --> 00:17:48,400
<font color="#ffffff">Hey.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

222
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:50,640
<font color="#ffffff">Once you get a boyfriend,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

223
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:52,880
<font color="#ffffff">you'll forget all about me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

224
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:54,720
<font color="#ffffff">Not true.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

225
00:17:54,800 --> 00:17:57,280
<font color="#ffffff">I'll never find any man better than you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

226
00:18:00,280 --> 00:18:01,720
<font color="#ffffff">-Watch out!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Oh.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

227
00:18:07,040 --> 00:18:09,040
<font color="#ffffff">Hi, guys!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

228
00:18:09,120 --> 00:18:10,960
<font color="#ffffff">Where did you get your license, uncle?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

229
00:18:11,040 --> 00:18:11,960
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, dear!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

230
00:18:12,040 --> 00:18:13,240
<font color="#ffffff">Girl!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

231
00:18:13,320 --> 00:18:15,440
<font color="#ffffff">You can't be ugly and mean.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

232
00:18:15,520 --> 00:18:17,920
<font color="#ffffff">Who are you? Why are you here, uncle?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

233
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:20,520
<font color="#ffffff">Girl, call me uncle again,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">and I'll slap the ugliness off your face.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

234
00:18:20,600 --> 00:18:22,480
<font color="#ffffff">Calm down, both of you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

235
00:18:22,560 --> 00:18:24,680
<font color="#ffffff">You don't even know each other.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Why are you fighting?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

236
00:18:24,760 --> 00:18:25,960
<font color="#ffffff">Who said that?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

237
00:18:26,040 --> 00:18:27,160
<font color="#ffffff">I know you, Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

238
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:29,400
<font color="#ffffff">But you don't know me yet.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

239
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:32,520
<font color="#ffffff">Confused?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

240
00:18:33,080 --> 00:18:36,920
<font color="#ffffff">Let me explain. I am the artist manager</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">for SP Entertainment.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

241
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:40,240
<font color="#ffffff">And I've been assigned</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to take care of you, Petch.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

242
00:18:40,320 --> 00:18:41,600
<font color="#ffffff">Take care of me?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

243
00:18:43,080 --> 00:18:43,920
<font color="#ffffff">About what?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

244
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:46,440
<font color="#ffffff">If you want to know,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">you should follow me, dear.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

245
00:18:51,120 --> 00:18:55,280
<font color="#ffffff">How is it? Spacious, spectacular,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">absolutely fabulous, right?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

246
00:18:55,360 --> 00:18:58,200
<font color="#ffffff">Just bring one bag,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">and you're ready to move right in.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

247
00:18:58,280 --> 00:19:00,400
<font color="#ffffff">It's so beautiful.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

248
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:02,320
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not dreaming, right?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

249
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:04,320
<font color="#ffffff">This is absolutely real, girl.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

250
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:07,560
<font color="#ffffff">Girl!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

251
00:19:10,600 --> 00:19:12,040
<font color="#ffffff">Wait for me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

252
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:17,320
<font color="#ffffff">Well? Beautiful, right?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

253
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:19,920
<font color="#ffffff">There's even a hot tub.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

254
00:19:20,520 --> 00:19:22,000
<font color="#ffffff">Perfect.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

255
00:19:22,080 --> 00:19:23,640
<font color="#ffffff">I can keep goldfish in it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

256
00:19:24,280 --> 00:19:27,160
<font color="#ffffff">You country girl.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Who keeps goldfish in here?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

257
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:29,800
<font color="#ffffff">This is a hot tub.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Do you even know what that is?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

258
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:31,760
<font color="#ffffff">I know. I'm not stupid.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

259
00:19:31,840 --> 00:19:34,240
<font color="#ffffff">But bathing like this</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">is a waste of resources.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

260
00:19:34,320 --> 00:19:36,680
<font color="#ffffff">You just brought me here</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to see this condo, right?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

261
00:19:37,320 --> 00:19:38,640
<font color="#ffffff">Can we leave now?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

262
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:43,840
<font color="#ffffff">Petch. Wait.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

263
00:19:45,400 --> 00:19:48,440
<font color="#ffffff">Wait! Hold on!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

264
00:19:49,040 --> 00:19:53,240
<font color="#ffffff">I didn't just show off this place.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">You're going to be living here too.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

265
00:19:54,640 --> 00:19:55,680
<font color="#ffffff">Here?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

266
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:57,760
<font color="#ffffff">What do you mean?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

267
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:00,240
<font color="#ffffff">Exactly.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

268
00:20:00,840 --> 00:20:02,160
<font color="#ffffff">You're not messing with us, right?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

269
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:05,920
<font color="#ffffff">Manager Kang never messes around.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

270
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:11,040
<font color="#ffffff">Everything you see here is totally free.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">The company is paying for all of it.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

271
00:20:12,520 --> 00:20:15,520
<font color="#ffffff">Wow! That's insane!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

272
00:20:15,600 --> 00:20:17,840
<font color="#ffffff">We'll finally have</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">a nice place to live in, Petch!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

273
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:20,440
<font color="#ffffff">Hey, hold on.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

274
00:20:20,520 --> 00:20:22,160
<font color="#ffffff">Save your excitement for now.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

275
00:20:22,240 --> 00:20:24,720
<font color="#ffffff">Because that's not all.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

276
00:20:24,800 --> 00:20:26,160
<font color="#ffffff">Ta-da!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

277
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:29,600
<font color="#ffffff">Brand new car</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">straight out of the showroom!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

278
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:35,120
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, my god!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

279
00:20:39,320 --> 00:20:41,400
<font color="#ffffff">This is beyond insane!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

280
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:44,360
<font color="#ffffff">Is this car really for Petch?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

281
00:20:44,440 --> 00:20:46,200
<font color="#ffffff">For sure.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

282
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:50,800
<font color="#ffffff">Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

283
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:52,760
<font color="#ffffff">Now that you have a car,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

284
00:20:52,840 --> 00:20:56,080
<font color="#ffffff">your passenger princess</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">can't be anyone but me.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

285
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:59,560
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, please! Passenger princess?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

286
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:02,200
<font color="#ffffff">What kind of princess is so clingy?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

287
00:21:02,280 --> 00:21:03,200
<font color="#ffffff">Kang.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

288
00:21:03,280 --> 00:21:05,880
<font color="#ffffff">If you hadn't just brought us a car,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I would've punched you.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

289
00:21:05,960 --> 00:21:07,280
<font color="#ffffff">-Want to try me?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Help!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

290
00:21:07,360 --> 00:21:09,760
<font color="#ffffff">Kang, wait. Hold on. Stop messing around.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

291
00:21:09,840 --> 00:21:11,120
<font color="#ffffff">We need to talk.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

292
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:16,280
<font color="#ffffff">Do you have any problems?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

293
00:21:16,360 --> 00:21:18,920
<font color="#ffffff">The condo, the car…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

294
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:20,960
<font color="#ffffff">Isn't it too much?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

295
00:21:21,040 --> 00:21:22,960
<font color="#ffffff">Just take what the company gives you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

296
00:21:23,040 --> 00:21:26,480
<font color="#ffffff">You're lucky that Natedao</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">is overseeing this project.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

297
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:32,600
<font color="#ffffff">Does that mean</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Natedao approved all of this for me?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

298
00:21:32,680 --> 00:21:33,880
<font color="#ffffff">Yes, exactly!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

299
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:36,600
<font color="#ffffff">You're extremely lucky it's Natedao.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

300
00:21:36,680 --> 00:21:39,480
<font color="#ffffff">If it were Akekaphol,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">let me tell you, it would be garbage.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

301
00:21:39,560 --> 00:21:41,640
<font color="#ffffff">You wouldn't be getting any of this.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

302
00:21:47,120 --> 00:21:50,400
<font color="#ffffff">You can't go in there. Excuse me. Hold on.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

303
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:52,960
<font color="#ffffff">It's fine. I'll talk to him myself.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

304
00:22:01,520 --> 00:22:03,880
<font color="#ffffff">Looks like you have</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">something important to say.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

305
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:04,800
<font color="#ffffff">Go ahead then.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

306
00:22:10,760 --> 00:22:12,000
<font color="#ffffff">Take them back.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

307
00:22:14,280 --> 00:22:16,200
<font color="#ffffff">I figured you would be arrogant like this.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

308
00:22:17,360 --> 00:22:18,280
<font color="#ffffff">It's not my arrogance.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

309
00:22:19,560 --> 00:22:21,240
<font color="#ffffff">A car, a condo,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

310
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:23,080
<font color="#ffffff">anyone would want them.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

311
00:22:23,920 --> 00:22:26,000
<font color="#ffffff">But they should come</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">from my own hard work,<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

312
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:28,320
<font color="#ffffff">not because of some special privilege.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

313
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:31,560
<font color="#ffffff">Wait.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

314
00:22:33,760 --> 00:22:35,200
<font color="#ffffff">Let's get this straight first.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

315
00:22:37,080 --> 00:22:39,120
<font color="#ffffff">This is an investment by the company.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

316
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:40,480
<font color="#ffffff">Nothing is given for free.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

317
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:43,080
<font color="#ffffff">What are you doing? Let go.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

318
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:47,040
<font color="#ffffff">Did you think you could throw money at me</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">and I would be your obedient little pet?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

319
00:22:47,120 --> 00:22:48,240
<font color="#ffffff">Are you crazy?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

320
00:22:49,240 --> 00:22:50,280
<font color="#ffffff">It's you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

321
00:22:50,360 --> 00:22:55,000
<font color="#ffffff">A generous capitalist, tossing money</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">at a desperate, lovesick singer.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

322
00:22:58,320 --> 00:22:59,600
<font color="#ffffff">Pull yourself together.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

323
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:04,040
<font color="#ffffff">All of this isn't because</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I've fallen for you.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

324
00:23:05,080 --> 00:23:07,080
<font color="#ffffff">It's strictly for the company's benefit.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

325
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:14,440
<font color="#ffffff">The condo belongs to Mr. Sompob.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

326
00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:17,920
<font color="#ffffff">He's letting you stay there</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">so it will be convenient for making music.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

327
00:23:19,080 --> 00:23:20,280
<font color="#ffffff">As for the car,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

328
00:23:20,360 --> 00:23:25,320
<font color="#ffffff">it's a company car lent to you</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">for the duration of your contract.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

329
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:29,320
<font color="#ffffff">Just take them.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

330
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:32,840
<font color="#ffffff">And do your duty as a good singer</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to repay the company and Mr. Sompob.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

331
00:23:35,360 --> 00:23:36,920
<font color="#ffffff">Another important thing.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

332
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:38,320
<font color="#ffffff">I already have a fiancé.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

333
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:41,920
<font color="#ffffff">If I didn't have to take responsibility</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">in Ake's place,<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

334
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:44,120
<font color="#ffffff">I wouldn't want to be in your way.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

335
00:24:07,640 --> 00:24:09,120
<font color="#ffffff">You're crazy.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

