00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:44,360
<font color="#ffffff">Petch, I got chased by a stray dog.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

495
00:35:44,440 --> 00:35:48,600
<font color="#ffffff"><i>The food I bought got completely ruined.</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I have to go buy it again.</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

496
00:35:48,680 --> 00:35:49,880
<font color="#ffffff">Don't bother.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

497
00:35:50,680 --> 00:35:52,680
<font color="#ffffff">We can buy new food.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

498
00:35:53,240 --> 00:35:55,280
<font color="#ffffff">But are you safe?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

499
00:35:58,600 --> 00:36:00,280
<font color="#ffffff">Are you worried about me, Petch?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

500
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:03,840
<font color="#ffffff">How could I not be worried, Sai?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">We only have each other.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

501
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:07,240
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, my! I'm blushing!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

502
00:36:07,320 --> 00:36:10,360
<font color="#ffffff">What are you talking about, Sai?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I don't understand.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

503
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:14,440
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, come on!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">You said you were worried about me.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

504
00:36:14,520 --> 00:36:16,800
<font color="#ffffff">It makes me smile from ear to ear.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

505
00:36:16,880 --> 00:36:22,000
<font color="#ffffff">Stop joking around.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Did you call me for a reason?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

506
00:36:23,120 --> 00:36:26,080
<font color="#ffffff">It's nothing.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

507
00:36:26,160 --> 00:36:28,000
<font color="#ffffff">I just wanted you to know</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

508
00:36:28,080 --> 00:36:31,280
<font color="#ffffff">that no matter how awful I am</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to the rest of the world,<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

509
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:34,040
<font color="#ffffff">I will only ever show you my good side.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

510
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:39,640
<font color="#ffffff">Petch, please trust me.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I will never betray you.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

511
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:44,440
<font color="#ffffff">You're talking weird, Sai.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">If something is wrong, just tell me.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

512
00:36:47,800 --> 00:36:52,640
<font color="#ffffff">You little…</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">You hung up before I could even finish.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

513
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:59,120
<font color="#ffffff"><i>You don't need to know</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>what I've been through.</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

514
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:02,480
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I just want you to know</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

515
00:37:02,560 --> 00:37:04,640
<font color="#ffffff"><i>that I love you more than anything,</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

516
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:07,760
<font color="#ffffff"><i>and I will always be by your side.</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

517
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:22,040
<font color="#ffffff">-Hello.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Hello, Petch. What's up?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

518
00:37:24,040 --> 00:37:25,080
<font color="#ffffff">The full package.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

519
00:37:25,160 --> 00:37:28,160
<font color="#ffffff">I'll get it looking pristine for you.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">But you'll have to wait a bit.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

520
00:37:28,240 --> 00:37:30,080
<font color="#ffffff">A car just came in a moment ago.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

521
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:34,040
<font color="#ffffff">-No problem.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Okay, I'll make it perfect. Take a seat.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

522
00:37:34,640 --> 00:37:36,960
<font color="#ffffff">-Hey.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Yes?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

523
00:37:37,040 --> 00:37:37,920
<font color="#ffffff">Is this your boy?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

524
00:37:38,000 --> 00:37:40,120
<font color="#ffffff">Yeah, my eldest son.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

525
00:37:40,840 --> 00:37:42,840
<font color="#ffffff">He's gorgeous.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

526
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:44,480
<font color="#ffffff">Do you want to give it a try?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

527
00:37:46,120 --> 00:37:47,800
<font color="#ffffff">You read my mind.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

528
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:52,040
<font color="#ffffff">With a big engine like this,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">revving it up must feel amazing.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

529
00:37:52,120 --> 00:37:53,200
<font color="#ffffff">Exactly.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

530
00:37:55,640 --> 00:37:59,960
<font color="#ffffff">Take it for a ride.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I'll get some work done while you wait.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

531
00:38:00,040 --> 00:38:02,200
<font color="#ffffff">-Thank you so much.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Sure thing.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

532
00:38:27,320 --> 00:38:29,200
<font color="#ffffff">My respects, Venerable Grandfather.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

533
00:38:29,280 --> 00:38:31,320
<font color="#ffffff">Blessings.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

534
00:38:31,400 --> 00:38:35,680
<font color="#ffffff">Natedao, what brings you here today?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

535
00:38:36,280 --> 00:38:38,920
<font color="#ffffff">It has been a long time</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">since I last visited.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

536
00:38:39,000 --> 00:38:42,400
<font color="#ffffff">Plus, I wanted to make</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">a merit offering for Damrong.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

537
00:38:43,600 --> 00:38:45,280
<font color="#ffffff">Bless you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

538
00:38:46,160 --> 00:38:48,240
<font color="#ffffff">Damrong must be happy</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

539
00:38:48,320 --> 00:38:51,800
<font color="#ffffff">to know someone still thinks of him</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">even after he's gone.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

540
00:38:51,880 --> 00:38:56,440
<font color="#ffffff">Even though Damrong has passed away,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">his memory as a good friend remains.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

541
00:38:57,240 --> 00:39:00,520
<font color="#ffffff">That is very touching, Natedao.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

542
00:39:00,600 --> 00:39:04,440
<font color="#ffffff">I think about Damrong all the time too.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

543
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:06,920
<font color="#ffffff">All right.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

544
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:09,560
<font color="#ffffff">Let's begin the ceremony, shall we?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

545
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:13,120
<font color="#ffffff">Let us recite the Five Precepts.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

546
00:39:57,160 --> 00:40:00,280
<font color="#ffffff">Making merit really fills me</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">with positive energy, Venerable.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

547
00:40:00,360 --> 00:40:01,840
<font color="#ffffff">Indeed.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

548
00:40:01,920 --> 00:40:05,960
<font color="#ffffff">Inner strength is essential</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">for moving forward in life.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

549
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:07,400
<font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

550
00:40:08,200 --> 00:40:11,080
<font color="#ffffff">If Damrong's spirit can perceive this,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

551
00:40:11,160 --> 00:40:14,200
<font color="#ffffff">I want him to feel</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">as good as I do right now.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

552
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:16,880
<font color="#ffffff">Natedao.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

553
00:40:17,440 --> 00:40:19,760
<font color="#ffffff">Good thoughts, good deeds.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

554
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:25,080
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, Natedao. Where did Petch go?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

555
00:40:25,160 --> 00:40:27,120
<font color="#ffffff">Why didn't you two come together?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

556
00:40:29,840 --> 00:40:34,960
<font color="#ffffff">Usually, Petch never misses</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">this kind of thing.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

557
00:40:35,640 --> 00:40:37,360
<font color="#ffffff">Did you two have a fight?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

558
00:40:39,040 --> 00:40:39,920
<font color="#ffffff">Venerable?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

559
00:40:41,080 --> 00:40:42,640
<font color="#ffffff">Are you here, Venerable?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

560
00:40:42,720 --> 00:40:45,520
<font color="#ffffff">Well, there you are.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

561
00:40:45,600 --> 00:40:47,280
<font color="#ffffff">Come in, Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

562
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:48,920
<font color="#ffffff">Why are you just standing there?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

563
00:40:49,000 --> 00:40:50,080
<font color="#ffffff">Come on in.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

564
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:58,840
<font color="#ffffff">My respects, Venerable.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

565
00:40:58,920 --> 00:41:00,360
<font color="#ffffff">Blessings.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

566
00:41:01,320 --> 00:41:02,920
<font color="#ffffff">I thought you weren't coming.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

567
00:41:03,720 --> 00:41:09,040
<font color="#ffffff">I was just asking Natedao</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">where you disappeared to.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

568
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:16,000
<font color="#ffffff">Well, in that case,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I should take my leave now, Venerable.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

569
00:41:16,080 --> 00:41:18,360
<font color="#ffffff">What's the rush?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

570
00:41:18,440 --> 00:41:19,840
<font color="#ffffff">Petch just got here.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

571
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:26,160
<font color="#ffffff">Maybe he wants to have</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">a private chat with you.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

572
00:41:26,240 --> 00:41:28,680
<font color="#ffffff">It's better if I don't intrude.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

573
00:41:28,760 --> 00:41:31,200
<font color="#ffffff">Blessings to you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

574
00:41:33,480 --> 00:41:35,320
<font color="#ffffff">Take care.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

575
00:41:43,040 --> 00:41:44,080
<font color="#ffffff">Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

576
00:41:44,720 --> 00:41:47,200
<font color="#ffffff">Something smells a bit fishy.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

577
00:41:47,800 --> 00:41:52,920
<font color="#ffffff">Have you and Natedao had a falling out?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

578
00:41:54,960 --> 00:41:57,240
<font color="#ffffff">She's my boss at work now, Venerable.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

579
00:41:57,320 --> 00:41:59,480
<font color="#ffffff">How could I possibly dare</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to have a problem with her?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

580
00:42:17,800 --> 00:42:19,560
<font color="#ffffff">What are you doing? Let go.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

581
00:42:19,640 --> 00:42:23,520
<font color="#ffffff">Did you think you could throw money at me</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">and I would be your obedient little pet?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

582
00:42:23,600 --> 00:42:25,000
<font color="#ffffff">Are you crazy?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

583
00:42:25,520 --> 00:42:26,720
<font color="#ffffff">It's you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

584
00:42:26,800 --> 00:42:31,520
<font color="#ffffff">A generous capitalist, tossing money</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">at a desperate, lovesick singer.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

585
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:04,240
<font color="#ffffff">Pull yourself together.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

586
00:43:04,840 --> 00:43:08,880
<font color="#ffffff">All of this isn't because</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I've fallen for you.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

587
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:11,400
<font color="#ffffff">It's strictly for the company's benefit.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

588
00:43:11,480 --> 00:43:13,360
<font color="#ffffff">I already have a fiancé.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

589
00:43:14,240 --> 00:43:16,720
<font color="#ffffff">If I didn't have to take responsibility</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">in Ake's place,<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

590
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:18,880
<font color="#ffffff">I wouldn't want to be in your way.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

591
00:43:24,920 --> 00:43:25,760
<font color="#ffffff">Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

592
00:43:26,440 --> 00:43:27,960
<font color="#ffffff">Didn't you say you were heading back?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

593
00:43:28,040 --> 00:43:30,920
<font color="#ffffff">Why are you still carrying</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">the weight of the world here?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

594
00:43:33,400 --> 00:43:35,560
<font color="#ffffff">I thought I could hide it from you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

595
00:43:36,480 --> 00:43:38,600
<font color="#ffffff">But you caught me anyway.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

596
00:43:40,120 --> 00:43:42,120
<font color="#ffffff">If something is bothering you,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

597
00:43:42,200 --> 00:43:44,320
<font color="#ffffff">you can tell me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

598
00:43:45,520 --> 00:43:49,280
<font color="#ffffff">It's not exactly like that. It's just…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

599
00:43:50,800 --> 00:43:51,960
<font color="#ffffff">Well…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

600
00:43:52,560 --> 00:43:54,240
<font color="#ffffff">I don't know how to start.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

601
00:43:55,000 --> 00:43:57,560
<font color="#ffffff">Sometimes, it feels like I've moved on,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

602
00:43:57,640 --> 00:43:59,400
<font color="#ffffff">but I mess up every single time,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

603
00:44:00,240 --> 00:44:02,440
<font color="#ffffff">to the point where I don't know</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">what to do anymore.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

604
00:44:03,480 --> 00:44:09,040
<font color="#ffffff">I don't know who you're talking about</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">or what exactly happened.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

605
00:44:09,720 --> 00:44:13,320
<font color="#ffffff">But everything depends on</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">your own heart, Petch.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

606
00:44:14,360 --> 00:44:16,080
<font color="#ffffff">Stop running away from your problems.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

607
00:44:17,120 --> 00:44:19,720
<font color="#ffffff">Otherwise, you'll never find the wisdom.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

608
00:44:19,800 --> 00:44:20,960
<font color="#ffffff">Understood, Venerable.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

609
00:44:22,080 --> 00:44:25,560
<font color="#ffffff">Yes. If I have a choice,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I won't run away again.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

610
00:44:26,160 --> 00:44:28,200
<font color="#ffffff">I will keep your words in mind.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

611
00:44:29,560 --> 00:44:31,000
<font color="#ffffff">Blessings.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

612
00:44:44,640 --> 00:44:45,800
<font color="#ffffff">What?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

613
00:44:46,480 --> 00:44:47,800
<font color="#ffffff">What's wrong with my car?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

614
00:45:34,200 --> 00:45:35,320
<font color="#ffffff">What's wrong?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

615
00:45:37,120 --> 00:45:38,560
<font color="#ffffff">I don't know.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

616
00:45:38,640 --> 00:45:40,840
<font color="#ffffff">If I knew,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">it wouldn't be broken down like this.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

617
00:45:42,000 --> 00:45:43,120
<font color="#ffffff">Let me take a look.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

618
00:45:43,200 --> 00:45:44,240
<font color="#ffffff">No need.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

619
00:45:47,920 --> 00:45:49,720
<font color="#ffffff">It's not like I want to get involved.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

620
00:45:50,240 --> 00:45:52,640
<font color="#ffffff">But you parked here,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">blocking traffic like this.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

621
00:45:53,280 --> 00:45:54,600
<font color="#ffffff">It'll cause trouble.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

622
00:45:55,360 --> 00:45:58,920
<font color="#ffffff">I don't want pessimists saying</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I can't do anything right,<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

623
00:45:59,000 --> 00:46:01,400
<font color="#ffffff">that I have to keep relying on people</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">who don't even want to help.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

624
00:46:02,080 --> 00:46:03,120
<font color="#ffffff">Look.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

625
00:46:03,200 --> 00:46:06,320
<font color="#ffffff">Throw your pride</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to the side of the road for a second.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

626
00:46:06,880 --> 00:46:07,760
<font color="#ffffff">Let me look at it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

627
00:46:17,880 --> 00:46:19,200
<font color="#ffffff">When was the car last checked?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

628
00:46:19,800 --> 00:46:22,360
<font color="#ffffff">I don't know. I just drive it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

629
00:46:22,440 --> 00:46:23,960
<font color="#ffffff">No wonder.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

630
00:46:24,040 --> 00:46:24,960
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, sorry.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

631
00:46:25,480 --> 00:46:26,440
<font color="#ffffff">I forgot.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

632
00:46:27,720 --> 00:46:28,840
<font color="#ffffff">You're a spoiled princess.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

633
00:46:29,440 --> 00:46:31,600
<font color="#ffffff">Is this really the time to insult me?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

634
00:46:31,680 --> 00:46:33,560
<font color="#ffffff">Did I hire you to fix it?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

635
00:46:35,080 --> 00:46:36,160
<font color="#ffffff">Unbelievable.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

636
00:46:37,000 --> 00:46:38,760
<font color="#ffffff">No good deed goes unpunished.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

637
00:46:38,840 --> 00:46:42,200
<font color="#ffffff">Look. If you don't know</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">how to fix it, just back off.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

638
00:46:42,280 --> 00:46:43,240
<font color="#ffffff">Ouch!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

639
00:46:51,080 --> 00:46:52,200
<font color="#ffffff">Does it still burn?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

640
00:46:56,080 --> 00:46:58,080
<font color="#ffffff">What are you doing?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

641
00:46:58,160 --> 00:47:00,480
<font color="#ffffff">Is this some new first-aid technique?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

642
00:47:02,160 --> 00:47:03,400
<font color="#ffffff">Well, is it working?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

643
00:47:04,960 --> 00:47:06,280
<font color="#ffffff">Very clever.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

644
00:47:07,560 --> 00:47:09,480
<font color="#ffffff">Just don't be so clumsy next time.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

645
00:47:10,080 --> 00:47:13,360
<font color="#ffffff">Hey. Are you here to fix my car</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">or lecture me?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

646
00:47:15,120 --> 00:47:16,720
<font color="#ffffff">I can do both at the same time.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

647
00:47:23,040 --> 00:47:24,120
<font color="#ffffff">Show-off.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

648
00:47:26,640 --> 00:47:27,520
<font color="#ffffff">Of course.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

649
00:47:31,760 --> 00:47:33,160
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, wow.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

650
00:47:33,240 --> 00:47:35,080
<font color="#ffffff">Are those mosquitoes or just you bragging?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

651
00:47:35,160 --> 00:47:36,800
<font color="#ffffff">Buzzing all over the place.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

652
00:47:40,760 --> 00:47:42,360
<font color="#ffffff">The fuel line snapped.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

653
00:47:43,320 --> 00:47:45,080
<font color="#ffffff">I can't fix it without spare parts.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

654
00:47:46,640 --> 00:47:48,720
<font color="#ffffff">I knew we would have to call a mechanic.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

655
00:48:26,240 --> 00:48:27,920
<font color="#ffffff">What seems to be the problem with the car?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

656
00:48:28,000 --> 00:48:29,560
<font color="#ffffff">The fuel line snapped.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

657
00:48:35,800 --> 00:48:36,960
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, that's completely torn.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

658
00:48:38,440 --> 00:48:40,680
<font color="#ffffff">Better call a tow truck</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to get it from here.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

659
00:48:41,400 --> 00:48:42,240
<font color="#ffffff">All right.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

660
00:49:00,320 --> 00:49:01,360
<font color="#ffffff">Where are you going?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

661
00:49:04,360 --> 00:49:05,400
<font color="#ffffff">Home.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

662
00:49:06,480 --> 00:49:07,600
<font color="#ffffff">I'll drop you off.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

663
00:49:07,680 --> 00:49:09,760
<font color="#ffffff">I told you I can go back by myself.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

664
00:49:12,560 --> 00:49:14,000
<font color="#ffffff">Getting a ride alone. Not scared?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

665
00:49:16,160 --> 00:49:17,520
<font color="#ffffff">That's my business.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

666
00:49:23,760 --> 00:49:25,000
<font color="#ffffff">Can you stop being so stubborn?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

667
00:50:09,120 --> 00:50:10,200
<font color="#ffffff">NEXT EPISODE</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

668
00:50:10,280 --> 00:50:12,440
<font color="#ffffff">-Ake.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Your lover?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

669
00:50:13,520 --> 00:50:14,440
<font color="#ffffff">Dao.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

670
00:50:16,320 --> 00:50:17,680
<font color="#ffffff">Damn it, Petch!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

671
00:50:18,960 --> 00:50:20,600
<font color="#ffffff">I will never let you win.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

672
00:50:20,680 --> 00:50:22,480
<font color="#ffffff">Dad!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

673
00:50:23,320 --> 00:50:26,920
<font color="#ffffff">-Those are his shoes.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-No way. He wouldn't commit suicide.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

674
00:50:27,000 --> 00:50:28,680
<font color="#ffffff">Dad.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

675
00:50:40,320 --> 00:50:45,120
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I wish I knew if I ever crossed your mind</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

676
00:50:46,360 --> 00:50:51,520
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I wish I knew if you heard the whisper</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

677
00:50:52,280 --> 00:50:58,240
<font color="#ffffff"><i>For my heart is crying out my love</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>It's deep and true</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

678
00:50:58,320 --> 00:51:03,040
<font color="#ffffff"><i>But never reaching you</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

679
00:51:04,320 --> 00:51:09,120
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I know that it simply cannot be</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

680
00:51:10,320 --> 00:51:15,440
<font color="#ffffff"><i>And I never want to cause you misery</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

681
00:51:16,720 --> 00:51:22,040
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I'm just an ordinary man</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Worth nothing at all</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

682
00:51:22,640 --> 00:51:28,080
<font color="#ffffff"><i>And I never want to make</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Your teardrops fall</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

683
00:51:29,160 --> 00:51:33,640
<font color="#ffffff"><i>You are out of reach</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

684
00:51:34,360 --> 00:51:39,800
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Is it a crime that I need you?</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

685
00:51:41,320 --> 00:51:45,520
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Please let me know for sure</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

686
00:51:46,320 --> 00:51:51,480
<font color="#ffffff"><i>That you're the one I've been waiting for</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

687
00:51:52,320 --> 00:51:56,640
<font color="#ffffff"><i>How much longer can I bear this pain?</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

688
00:51:58,320 --> 00:52:03,320
<font color="#ffffff"><i>How much longer must I wait in vain?</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

689
00:52:04,320 --> 00:52:09,280
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I really don't know what move to make</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

690
00:52:10,320 --> 00:52:16,320
<font color="#ffffff"><i>To end this heartache</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>And say that I love you</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

691
00:52:16,400 --> 00:52:17,760
<font color="#ffffff">Subtitle translation by: Sarunpon T.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>
